title: GATE Cut-offs needed to get into IITs, NITs, etc - GeeksQuiz
text:
Interview Corner GATE Cut-offs needed to get into IITs, NITs, etc 
We have tried compiling the cut-off scores of various IITs, NITs and other good Institutes for post graduate programs. These cut-off scores will help you to set a goal which you need to achieve for getting admissions in the respective institutes. 
The data here is based on previous year. Marks are with approximation. 
1. IISC Bangalore (M.Tech Program) General
